cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CR 

The paper focuses on the use of IoT architecture for monitoring in dynamic environments, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed algorithm for following mobile targets/individuals involves self-organization and self-optimization properties, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the security aspects of the proposed system, which could be relevant to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
